-- Ukraine to Buy 26 Billion Cubic Meters of Gas: Kurier
-- B y   K a t e r y n a   C h o u r s i n a
-- 2012-11-23T09:07:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-23/ukraine-to-buy-26-billion-cubic-meters-of-gas-kurier.html
Ukraine will buy 26 billion cubic
meters of natural gas from Russia this year, Uryadovyi Kurier,
an official government newspaper cited Energy and Coal Minister
 Yuriy Boyko  as saying.  Natural gas imports will decline in 2013 while Ukrainian
coal mines will produce 85 million metric tons of coal this
year, Kurier cited Boyko as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kateryna Choursina in Kiev at 
 kchoursina@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  